name: LAX VR
summary: LAX VR is the ultimate first-person VR lacrosse experience, offering both Box and Field lacrosse modes including a new exhilarating 6v6 field game where you can play as either a field player, long pole or goalie. Game modes include: Field, Box, Braveheart, Shooting, Goalie, Longstick, Shoot Around, and Wall Ball. Our Medicine Game mode pays tribute to the Indigenous People who created lacrosse, set in a mythical historic environment. Hone your skills, customize your twig, and have fun in the immersive...
